    "4 Both the sampling decisions and the level of coder agreement can impact the performance of automatic text analysis methods (Wang et al., 2022).",
    "Step 2: Method choice The next step is to choose a text mining method to analyze the whole textual corpus.",
    "We discuss several families of methods that can be used for this task.",
    "Dictionary methods Dictionary methods use word lists (dictionaries) to categorize texts.",
    "For instance, when identifying emotions in text, a dictionary would map words that correspond to each emotion, such as joy or surprise."
